WEBVTT

00:00:00.144 --> 00:00:01.464
Došla sam danas ovamo

00:00:01.464 --> 00:00:04.151
kako bih s vama razgovarala
o jednom problemu.

00:00:04.151 --> 00:00:07.678
To je vrlo jednostavan, no ipak razarajući problem.

00:00:07.678 --> 00:00:09.623
Raširen je po cijelom svijetu

00:00:09.623 --> 00:00:12.536
i utječe na sve nas.

00:00:12.536 --> 00:00:14.621
Problem su

00:00:14.621 --> 00:00:17.346
anonimne tvrtke.

00:00:17.346 --> 00:00:19.436
Zvuči vrlo suhoparno i tehnički,

00:00:19.436 --> 00:00:20.492
zar ne?

00:00:20.492 --> 00:00:22.994
No, anonimne vam tvrtke otežavaju

00:00:22.994 --> 00:00:25.546
i ponekad u potpunosti onemogućavaju

00:00:25.546 --> 00:00:27.395
da saznate

00:00:27.395 --> 00:00:30.394
koji su točno ljudi odgovorni